      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of alternative hemolysis model forms (power-law, strain-based, mechanistic) with Bayesian model selection; model form uncertainty quantified.",
      "rationale": "Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model was used. Alternative model forms were not evaluated. Model form uncertainty is unquantified. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
